==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ironing
<hw>I"ron*ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
or process of smoothing, as clothes, with hot flatirons.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The clothes ironed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Ironing board</b></col>, <cd>a flat board, upon which
clothes are laid while being ironed.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ironish</ent>⟦br⟧
